  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    Path Pioneer
    
    Create your own custom path — then walk it again to see it come to life.
    
    Path Pioneer is designed as a blueprint for building non-permanent paths that you can quickly recreate anywhere. Whether you're indoors, outdoors, or exploring a new space, you can design a flexible route that adapts to your surroundings.
    
    Customize this sample experience by shaping your own itinerary across any path you choose.
    
    How It Works
    
    Tap “OK” to begin creating your path.
    
    Set the starting point by placing a reference marker at the beginning of your route.
    
    Walk your desired path.
    
    When you reach your destination, place the end marker to complete the path setup.
    
    Experience Your Path
    
    Return to the starting point and walk the route again.
    
    As you move along the path you created, you’ll see the Path Completion HUD activate — guiding you and tracking your progress from start to finish.
    
    Create. Walk. Repeat.
